name: Boba Network x KaratDAO Consensus Party Pass

metadata.description:
We've partnered with our friends at KaratDAO to give Boba holders exclusive access to their party at Consensus 2022! Any holder of this Boba Network NFT will be granted access!

Requirement: A minimum of 10 $BOBA must be held in the user's wallet to be eligible to mint.

Details:
Saturday, June 11
Address: EDGE ROOFTBAR AT THE MARRIOT
110 E 2ND ST AUSTIN, TX 78701
7PM - 11PM

More info at https://elysium.karatdao.com/
